The Alex Jones Show
Tuesday, 23 July 2013


[sebaygo1]


Show Description
................

From the Infowars web site :: On the July 23 edition of The Alex Jones Show, Alex interviews the Houston New Black Panther Party leader and minister Quanell X about the recent pro-Trayvon protest he led through an upscale Houston, Texas neighborhood on Sunday. 

Alex will cover the latest violence erupting in Egypt following in the wake of the removal of Muslim Brotherhood leader Mohamed Mursi [sic], where hundreds of Mursi [sic] supporters clashed with local residents killing 6 and injuring 33. 

Alex will also discuss a new poll released by McClatchy Washington Bureau that reveals Obama's approval rating continues to decline following the rise of gasoline prices, revelations about domestic spying and more turmoil in the Middle East. Obama's job approval rating has sharply dropped from 50% last April to 41% today.
